        <div id="calendarContainer">
            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>üìã GitHub Pages - Ready to Use!</strong>
                This version works on GitHub Pages without any Azure AD setup.<br><br>
                <strong>Features:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>‚úÖ View your O365 calendar in themed weekly format</li>
                    <li>‚úÖ Automatic color-coding by meeting type</li>
                    <li>‚úÖ Week navigation and refresh</li>
                    <li>‚úÖ Works from any device with a browser</li>
                    <li>üìù Add/edit events in Outlook, refresh here to see updates</li>
                </ul>
                <strong>Getting Started:</strong> Click "Connect O365" above to sign in with your Microsoft account.
